# User Interface Module

## PURPOSE
All user-facing interface components and pages for the extension.
Handles user interactions, displays data, and manages UI state.

## STRUCTURE
- /popup: Main popup window (popup.html, popup.js, popup.css)
- /components: Reusable UI components
- /styles: Shared CSS styles

## CONTAINS
- Popup window with scan button
- Subscription list display with unsubscribe links
- Authentication/login UI
- Payment flow UI
- Settings page
- Loading states and error handling

## RESPONSIBILITIES
- Display scanned subscriptions
- Show unsubscribe links clearly
- Handle user authentication flow
- Trigger payment process
- Show free tier limits (5 subs)
- Provide feedback for user actions

## REFERENCES
- Parent: /src/.windsurf
- Root: /.windsurf
- Uses: /src/core/* for business logic, /src/api/* for backend calls

## RULES
- Keep UI simple and intuitive
- Show clear loading states
- Display errors user-friendly
- Make unsubscribe links prominent
- Responsive design for different screen sizes
- Accessibility (ARIA labels, keyboard navigation)
